snippet.title: Spyro: Enter the Dragonfly Definitive Edition (Mod Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
After 2 years in development, the Definitive Edition is finally ready for you to experience! This mod fixes hundreds upon hundreds of bugs, restores many pieces of unused and even cut content, and adds key quality of life improvements to make the experience better than ever.

Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qYu-TpzBFCBmSzzUx6dUo3eip1QjV9aa/view?usp=sharing
